            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top">
Goblin Market’s Allotropic Sisters
<span
 class="texto2">by <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue4/alan_wall/bio.php"
 class="link3">Alan Wall</a><br>
 </span></td>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
